snippet.title: Far Cry New Dawn - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Come back to hope County, 17 years after a global nuclear catastrophy. Discover a vibrant post-apolcalyptic world and face the scavengers and their ruthless leaders : the Twins. 

Far Cry New Dawn will be available on PS4, Xbox One and PC on February 15th, 2019

More info: www.farcrygame.com
